{"tid":853414,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【低處未算低】金獅僅售415萬 代理：唔係高位買就無事","createTime":"2018-10-08T14:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T12:44:38.000Z","uid":174649,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6e51609040ff94fe0d97904444b6f4f169950e87","tid":853414,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"二手樓劈極未見底，市場昨流傳大圍金獅花園金麗閣中層4室以420萬易手，惟最新消息指，正確成交價再平5萬元，低見415萬元，以單位實用面積270方呎計算，呎價15,370元，樓價回到今年2月水平。<br />\n<br />\n金豐閣中層5室，實用面積260方呎，今年8月以510萬元售出，呎價19,615元。今次最新成交，呎價短短兩個月下調22%。區內代理表示，金獅花園一向是跌市先鋒之一，「沙田第一城已跌穿500萬，金獅跌返去400萬係好合理」。金獅花園200餘呎單位曾升見500萬元，現跌至415萬元，該代理說，只是正常高位調整，「唔係高位買就無事」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181008/large/1538998406_55ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181008%2Flarge%2F1538998406_55ef.jpg&h=30733ba7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7939a868519e8ea155ff2989bc9bfcd0367c0956","tid":853414,"uid":195728,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33725653fdf1435eaeadbbbc056baf45d365932","tid":853414,"uid":131686,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e19c20faa71b96e8b09b453a0ad9d14734f454","tid":853414,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"幻覺黎o既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日高位, 明日低位, 只升不跌, 一買即賺"},{"pid":"ad7f02f9f599e76da5a27c787d4bfb38f274b39b","tid":853414,"uid":922,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"自住唔怕跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eb6353193d9194918c7ba9ef4102aeb69a2401","tid":853414,"uid":83582,"like":8,"dislike":0,